Name: Rabbit Canyon
About the game: You play the role of a brave hare running through a dangerous gorge. On the way you will meet mines, automatic turrets, birds of prey. Stones are scattered along the road and trees grow. Control a hare and dodge obstacles or jump over them. Run as far as you can and get the highest score. Happy running through the rabbit canyon!
